heading_context: Find out if someone has an attorney, deputy or guardian acting for them
chunks.html_content:
Apply to search the Office of the Public Guardian (OPG) registers to see if someone has another person acting on their behalf.

This can be:

  • an attorney under a lasting power of attorney
  • an attorney under an enduring power of attorney
  • a court appointed deputy
  • a guardian for someone who is missing appointed by the High Court
